                    "text": "20 feet. The colorful runes that decorate a d'ziriak's body create dim light. The natural bioluminescence is specially adapted to the Shadow Plane, able to overcome magical <a aonid=\"39\" game-obj=\"Traits\">darkness</a> as if it were magical <a aonid=\"100\" game-obj=\"Traits\">light</a> of the d'ziriak's level."
